00:54:24,240 --> 00:54:30,040
with that if you want to join this team," 
and totally fine if that's not for you.

616
00:54:30,040 --> 00:54:33,560
I love that. It makes me think of something 
when my colleague used to say to me is,  

617
00:54:33,560 --> 00:54:36,560
"If you haven't changed teams 
or your desk in six months,  

618
00:54:36,560 --> 00:54:39,240
something's about to happen. 
Something's about to change."

619
00:54:39,240 --> 00:54:40,120
Totally.

