business units, if you're functionally organized,  

658
00:58:09,840 --> 00:58:13,680
sometimes you create too many dependencies 
across the organization, and it becomes this  

659
00:58:13,680 --> 00:58:19,800
matrix way of working, which could be challenging 
and as a result could be slower to ship product. 

660
00:58:19,800 --> 00:58:24,640
Those are just examples. These are not 
universal issues, but those are examples  

661
00:58:24,640 --> 00:58:29,880
where regardless of how you're organized, 
there are going to be problems. So for me,  

662
00:58:29,880 --> 00:58:35,240
one learning was if you're having a problem 
and you're trying to solve this problem,  

663
00:58:35,240 --> 00:58:40,000
