00:59:24,560 --> 00:59:26,600
that stuff? Because there's people and 
then there's like, "Here's your goal,  

674
00:59:26,600 --> 00:59:30,560
here's how you're measured," and that's what 
they're going to work on in this thought.

675
00:59:30,560 --> 00:59:36,120
I mean, I think incentives come down to 
culture, and it's what you set as the  

